  "prompt": "How do you know if you have a crush on someone?",
  "response": "Having a crush on someone can feel both exciting and confusing! Here are some common signs that you might have a crush on someone:\n\n### 1. **You Think About Them Often**\n   - They pop into your mind frequently, even when you're not with them.\n   - You daydream about scenarios involving them.\n\n### 2. **You Get Nervous or Giddy Around Them**\n   - You feel butterflies in your stomach or your heart races when they\u2019re near.\n   - You might stumble over your words or act a little awkward.\n\n### 3. **You Want to Impress Them**\n   - You put extra effort into your appearance or behavior when you\u2019re around them.\n   - You want them to notice you in a positive way.\n\n### 4. **You Care Deeply About Their Opinions**\n   - Their approval or attention feels really important to you.\n   - You might overthink things they\u2019ve said or done.\n\n### 5. **You Feel Happy Just Being Around Them**\n   - Their presence brightens your day, even if you\u2019re just hanging out casually.\n   - You feel a sense of joy or excitement when they\u2019re nearby.\n\n### 6. **You Pay Extra Attention to Them**\n   - You notice small details about them, like their habits, preferences, or quirks.\n   - You\u2019re curious about their interests, hobbies, and life.\n\n### 7. **You Feel Jealous or Protective**\n   - You might feel a pang of jealousy if they show interest in someone else.\n   - You want to be the one they focus on.\n\n### 8. **You Imagine a Future with Them**\n   - You fantasize about spending time with them or being in a relationship.\n   - You find yourself wondering, \u201cWhat if we were together?\u201d\n\n### 9. **Their Personality or Looks Stand Out to You**\n   - You\u2019re especially drawn to their smile, laugh, voice, or mannerisms.\n   - You find them physically attractive in a way that stands out from others.\n\n### 10. **You Look for Opportunities to Spend Time with Them**\n   - You go out of your way to be around them or talk to them.\n   - You might make excuses to see or contact them.\n\n### 11. **You Feel a Connection**\n   - You feel like you \u201cclick\u201d with them on a deeper level.\n   - You\u2019re drawn to their energy or vibe.\n\nIf you\u2019re experiencing several of these signs, it\u2019s likely you have a crush! Remember, crushes are natural and can be a fun part of exploring your feelings. Take your time to understand what you\u2019re feeling and enjoy the process!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
